INSTALL
-------

0) Run sudo ./install-packages.sh (only once per server)
1) Install the package ciudades from https://github.com/sebasgoldberg/ciudades.git. (only once per server)
2) Run ./config.sh and apply your configuration.
3) Run ./install.sh (for iamcast).
4) Verify that /etc/apache2/ports.conf is configured correctly (remember to add 'NameVirtualHost *:<port>' for each used por in case that has multiple server on the same port).

UPGRADE (desde version 1.1)
---------------------------

- pull de iamcast
- pull de agencia
- <iamcast-folder> $ ./update.sh

UPGRADE (desde v1.0)
--------------------

- sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get upgrade
- pull de iamcast
- pull de agencia
- pull de cross
- unninstall django and install django 1.6.1: 
    sudo pip uninstall Django
    sudo pip install Django==1.6.1
- install Grappelli:
    pip install django-grappelli==2.5.1
- <iamcast-folder> $ sudo ./install-framework.sh
- cambiar configuración del sitio http y https:
    ...
    WSGIDaemonProcess iamcast[_ssl] python-path=/home/cerebro/iamcast/
    WSGIProcessGroup iamcast[_ssl]
    WSGIScriptAlias / /home/cerebro/iamcast//alternativa/wsgi.py
    ...
    Alias /static/admin/ /usr/local/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/grappelli/static/admin/
    ...
- actualizar alternativa/ambiente.py a nueva versión.
- swap the orther between admin and grappelli app in settings.py
- update static files:
    <iamcast-folder>/collectedstatic $ rm -rf *
    <iamcast-folder> $ ./manage.py collectstatic (from root folder)
- restore the orther between admin and grappelli app in settings.py
- sudo service apache2 restart
